<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Seckendorff zu Altheim</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt, dass die herausgegebenen vier Pferde und ein Fuhrwagen dem Peter Lutz und anderen Bürgern zu Nürnberg gehören.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_194" id="96v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_194_r2l1"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Seckendorf cʒü Altheım </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_194_r2l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Lucʒen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l3"><expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / wie Jr dem ſein hab <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / Alſo / daʒ ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l4">fricʒ Spanfarch vnſer <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> geredt hab / . daʒ er die vor vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l5"><expan>behab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſülle / . Alſo <expan>laʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiſſen / . daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein hab mitnamen vier pferd vnd einen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l7">wagen / . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_194_r1l1">vor vns cʒü </ab><ab facs="#facs_194_r1l2">den <expan>heılıge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_194_r1l3">behabt hat </ab></add> daʒ die ſein vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein / Alſo / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l8">weder ſein <expan>vat<ex>er</ex></expan> noch dhein <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> awſman <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemain </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l9">daran nicht hab <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd wir getrawen ew vvol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l10">Jr ſchont der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_194" id="96v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Seckendorf czü Altheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Luczen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie
                        ir dem sein hab <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, also daz ew Fricz Spanfarch, unser
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, geredt hab, daz er die vor uns
                                <expan>behab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sülle. Also
                            <expan>lazze<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        wissen, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein hab, mit namen vier pferd und einen
                        wagen, <add>vor uns czü den <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt
                            hat</add>, daz die sein und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> sein, also daz weder sein
                                <expan>vat<ex>er</ex></expan> noch dhein
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> awsman <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil
                        noch gemain daran nicht hab <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                        und wir getrawen ew wol, ir schont der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
